<p style="text-align:center;">The Harbour is also worth walking around, it&#8217;s very pretty.  Some scenes from the TV Series Poldark are filmed there.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">I took the opportunity to visit the Eden Project again.  There is always something new to see, it&#8217;s such a big site. This time I saw an Art Installation called Infinity Blue, a Giant stone Seed and a Gecko!</p>
