				<div class="post-2816 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blogroll tag-argentiere tag-baqueira-beret tag-canada tag-chamonix tag-france tag-haute-savoie tag-mont-blanc tag-mountains tag-off-piste tag-powder tag-pyrenees tag-ski tag-skiing tag-snow tag-spain tag-switzerland tag-valais tag-whistler tag-zermatt">
					<div class="entry">
					<p>Sometime last year, I hit a wall. Not literally, but I found I could no longer write this Blog. I took a break, in the hope that I would feel refreshed. My break took a little longer than expected, and I&#8217;m now playing catch up with my Blogging.</p>
