					<h2><a href="https://sunshack.wordpress.com/2017/09/02/wet/" rel="bookmark">Wet</a></h2>
				</div>
				<div class="post-2725 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blogroll tag-beach tag-bodmin tag-cornwall tag-eden-project tag-health tag-holiday tag-mawgan-porth tag-padstow tag-seaside tag-summer tag-surfing tag-tourism tag-tourist tag-truro tag-wakeboarding tag-watersports">
					<div class="entry">
					<p style="text-align:center;"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-2734" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040422.jpg?w=500&#038;h=375" alt="P1040422" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040422.jpg?w=500&amp;h=375 500w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040422.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=750 1000w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040422.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040422.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040422.jpg?w=768&amp;h=576 768w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"   /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">This summer I decided my Holiday would be activity based. I would be staying in the UK, and taking lessons in Surfing and Wakeboarding. I headed to Cornwall, and planned to split my time between lessons, Hiking and enjoying some Beach time. This was my view when I visited Newquay, and it was probably the best weather  I saw during my stay.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">I stayed in a lovely  <a href="https://www.seavista.co.uk/">B&amp;B</a> in the village of Mawgan Porth. My Surfing lessons were with <a href="http://www.kingsurf.co.uk/">Kingsurf</a> and I made good progress.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">So, no lazing on the Beach for me between lessons, I went sightseeing. I visited Truro on a Sunday, which was busy with Tourists.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2748 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040477.jpg?w=225&#038;h=300" alt="P1040477" width="225" height="300" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040477.jpg?w=225&amp;h=300 225w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040477.jpg?w=450&amp;h=600 450w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040477.jpg?w=113&amp;h=150 113w" sizes="(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2751 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040480.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="P1040480" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040480.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040480.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040480.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">I took a day to visit the <a href="http://www.edenproject.com/visit">Eden Project</a> near St Austell. It&#8217;s a great day out, and the Biodomes are full of wonderful plants, plus some Birds work there as Pest Controllers!</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2762 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040423.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="P1040423" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040423.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040423.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040423.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2769" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2769" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2769" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040466.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="P1040466" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040466.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040466.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040466.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2769" class="wp-caption-text">A Roul Roul at work in the Tropical Biodome</p></div>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2775 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040438.jpg?w=225&#038;h=300" alt="P1040438" width="225" height="300" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040438.jpg?w=225&amp;h=300 225w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040438.jpg?w=450&amp;h=600 450w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040438.jpg?w=113&amp;h=150 113w" sizes="(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px" /></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2780 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040453.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="P1040453" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040453.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040453.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040453.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2784 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040424.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="P1040424" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040424.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040424.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040424.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">The Eden Project was one of the few venues that I visited which offered free parking to visitors. I feel that I spent more on parking the car than I did on food during my stay in Cornwall.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">My Wakeboarding session was organised by <a href="http://www.lakeviewcornwall.co.uk/portfolio/wakepark/">Lakeview Wakepark</a> at Waterside Cornwall in the village of Lanivet near Bodmin. The Lake has a cable tow system for Wakeboarding.  The night before my lesson, I&#8217;d seriously stubbed a toe in the shower at my Hotel. I&#8217;m pleased to say that having a toe which subsequently turned out to be broken made no difference at all to my lesson. I had hoped to be able to make it to my feet (and stay there). I was pretty pleased with my progress.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class=" size-medium wp-image-2797 aligncenter" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040519.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="P1040519" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040519.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040519.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040519.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">I took a look around Padstow one day. A very pretty town and fishing port, though everywhere you turn, Chef Rick Stein has made his mark, either a shop/restaurant/Cafe. This has resulted in the nickname for the town being Padstein. The lanes leading to the town are quite narrow, I had to reverse about 100 metres to make way for a Double Decker Bus!.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2804" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2804" class="size-medium wp-image-2804" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040494.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040494.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040494.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040494.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2804" class="wp-caption-text">Yes, really!</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2806" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2806" class="size-medium wp-image-2806" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040487.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040487.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040487.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/p1040487.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2806" class="wp-caption-text">Pretty Harbour in Padstow</p></div>
					</div>
