			<div class="postwrapper wideposts" id="post-2591">
				<div class="title">
					<small>Posted by: <strong>sunshack</strong> | March 25, 2017 </small>
					<h2><a href="https://sunshack.wordpress.com/2017/03/25/windy-2/" rel="bookmark">Windy</a></h2>
				</div>
				<div class="post-2591 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blogroll tag-heritage tag-history tag-leisure tag-manston tag-spitfire tag-ww2">
					<div class="entry">
					<p style="text-align:center;">The Spitfire and Hurricane Memorial Trust Museum at Manston, Kent, had an open day recently. This was the 72nd Anniversary Event for the Manston Spitfire TB752. A variety of attractions were on offer to help raise funds for the Museum.  The Museum is really well organised with friendly staff and even had some exhibits available for visitors to handle.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2676" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2676" class="size-medium wp-image-2676" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040301.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040301.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040301.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040301.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2676" class="wp-caption-text">Spitfire at Manston</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2677" style="width: 235px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2677" class="wp-image-2677 size-medium" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040305.jpg?w=225&#038;h=300" alt="" width="225" height="300" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040305.jpg?w=225&amp;h=300 225w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040305.jpg?w=450&amp;h=600 450w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040305.jpg?w=113&amp;h=150 113w" sizes="(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2677" class="wp-caption-text">Spitfire Cockpit at Manston</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2679" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2679" class="wp-image-2679 size-medium" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040303.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040303.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040303.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040303.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2679" class="wp-caption-text">Browning Machine Gun fitted to Spitfires</p></div>
<p style="text-align:center;">In the adjoining Hangar sits a Hurricane. Really well presented and restored.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2681" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2681" class="size-medium wp-image-2681" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040310.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040310.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040310.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040310.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2681" class="wp-caption-text">Hurricane</p></div>
<p style="text-align:center;">I spent some time chatting to the staff, and they were very interested to hear about my experiences when  I flew in <a href="https://sunshack.wordpress.com/2016/11/05/spitfire/">Spitfire MJ627</a>  last year. The Spitfire, Spirit of Kent was due to attend, but cancelled on the day due to bad weather. Outside the venue, is a separate RAF Museum, which has a Doodlebug Bomb on display. Many of these V-1 bombs fell on London during WW2.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2685" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2685" class="size-medium wp-image-2685" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040315.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040315.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040315.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040315.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2685" class="wp-caption-text">Doodlebug</p></div>
<p style="text-align:center;">Listen to the sound of a <a href="https://youtu.be/Q1qsBGTkVSk">Doodlebug</a> passing overhead.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">Some really unusual Vintage Cars attended.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2692" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2692" class="size-medium wp-image-2692" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040294.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040294.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040294.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040294.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><p id="caption-attachment-2692" class="wp-caption-text">Austin 7 Super Speed</p></div>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2694" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040299.jpg?w=300&#038;h=241" alt="" width="300" height="241" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040299.jpg?w=300&amp;h=241 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040299.jpg?w=600&amp;h=482 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040299.jpg?w=150&amp;h=120 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2695" src="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040295.jpg?w=300&#038;h=225" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040295.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040295.jpg?w=600&amp;h=450 600w, https://sunshack.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/p1040295.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">The days before bicycle racks.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">By the time I left, it was not just windy, but really windy.</p>
